 ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Thursday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Julianna Conroy Singh", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXQZwen_7ECK1HL0RiyyXXyjiZO926WU06SwZ2JJTHTYs41RLS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "My partner and I went and played pickleball for the first time this morning and we had so much fun! The court is new and clean, and the owner is so welcoming and friendly🙏🏽 We rented the paddles and practice ball and it was really affordable. Plus such a great workout! They invited us to come back and play again, and we’re really excited to join😊", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3R8i6JfiBA_Yns2i0fBp0EFNuMYt2OUY-iH8DJZTJ8kQZIR0BLIms04Nr1pgLuLH1QKAhJme3vwvgpvjOX1Ef4KbMYEDqX-ZPaG4kLMoc9gw2dioeB60Z7omZ-HIvpGxpb0tgW=k-no"], "When": "2025-3-5"}, {"Name": "Sam North", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxjb0ZIdiSHftI0s4PWxuOdPMFh0GLnDqqLuf2SnE0Xo76xx9-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great little pickleball Center. 2 courts, friendly owner and locals, cheap court and paddle hire.", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Calvin Tran", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmz5Z3n5c03myDYftjHnO4Na_RwARxK4_4NEZe7Sjt28aUMA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Chỉ có hai sân những luôn đông đúc người chơi và rất vui, các bạn nhân viên ở đây rất thân thiện, giá rất hạt dẻ nữa.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2p2dpfn_By71bd87J43x2ZoiogjUuhh1OX445FzV477JH6yQrFH_-oCzwoqb4Ze6eCpcEHtu5hlb5WeLcDcqwJOXLtdZF1vHmN31PzfkvTWQaS3neJIqAHeiGY4yoNdk9TUM8OZQ=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Y83gyKVLTXfX7DhSpGVMRU78lkcFJiLef2tbGtP7a3066JMXUCHUHrKdmPHpZz2YgiFxO57P257B5i0feDvRS5h9x6PDfVIjRe7ipAoog48a0emKk-2CPOUTDxxwOSvIv4GW9=k-no"], "When": "2025-3-25"}, {"Name": "Thuận Trần Thanh", "ProfilePicture": "