–10 p.m."], "Thursday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Calvin Bui", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg7eRxH3dCtKC28Fo3Q_iI64zewK2TZXComES-g02W1TCnsX_ZCg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân Pickleball Hoàng Sâm in Da Nang is a hidden gem for sports enthusiasts—a vibrant hub where passion for pickleball meets community spirit. From the moment you step onto the pristine, well-maintained courts, you feel the electric buzz of energy and camaraderie in the air. This isn’t just a place to play; it’s a dynamic meeting ground where beginners and seasoned pros alike rally together, share high-fives, and push each other to new heights.\n\nThe facility boasts state-of-the-art equipment and immaculate playing surfaces that ensure every match is as smooth as it is exhilarating. Beyond the game, the welcoming staff and supportive atmosphere create a sense of belonging that makes every visit memorable. Whether you’re looking to perfect your serve, enjoy a friendly game, or simply soak in the contagious enthusiasm of the community, Sân Pickleball Hoàng Sâm offers an experience that’s both invigorating and fun.\n\nFor anyone in Da Nang eager to dive into a fast-paced, exciting sport with a side of genuine connection, this is the spot to be. Experience the thrill, the teamwork, and the pure joy of pickleball at Sân Pickleball Hoàng Sâm—you won’t regret it!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1VP3KeicNHaKsRJTj4qYDgaLOzXLcdDBuh7CBCvSB34y7G7rUWiES9iynJ28kDP0WfE035GfgshxR7GBADkU1RImKTjEBBNdiNqlHH21eZmihvxgqstT0tHZBUWLgg2VI56nsfHA=k-no"], "When": "2025-3-18"}, {"Name": "Đàm Thu Hiền", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3-H1ybK-kjvRc8b3IJH2S0P59bhRro5EVVfaeWMDrkCL79g_1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Service is good", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Minh Tuan Ngo", "ProfilePicture": "http